short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Sprint capacity view for leftover items

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: JiraSprintCapacityCalculator is a Chrome extension designed to streamline your workflow within Jira's sprint planning interface. The extension adds additional functionality to the sprint board, allowing users to easily manage leftover sprint tasks.
